{"tid":241961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一即係全，全即係一","createTime":"2017-05-13T14:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T18:53:04.000Z","uid":17058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e607686029355241a5898ee6c0773b91a98d0c4","tid":241961,"uid":17058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"其實意思係世界冇左你一個一樣會轉,但個世界就係因為有好多個你先會有呢個世界<br />\n唔可以冇左其中一樣<br />\n因為啱啱又loop鋼鍊一次,可能有滴滴1999"},{"pid":"7d351d721929705880f9e883a9b8c13ce5bc8f46","tid":241961,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:34:25.000Z","msg":"係咁解咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef142f2b73227b1a31983285e90a40314c79a73c","tid":241961,"uid":52178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實意思係世界冇左你一個一樣會轉,但個世界就係因為有好多個你先會有呢個世界<br />\n唔可以冇左其中一樣<br />\n因為啱啱又loop鋼鍊一次,可能有滴滴1999</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鋼鍊係咪有兩套動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得好細個睇個套同FA好似唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eebe34dd6c653ac1cfda238789cccde8bacb9a","tid":241961,"uid":17058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁解咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係唔太清楚想有高手指點下"},{"pid":"856ca90694e1b57acfb8970cffcaf626a38c15cf","tid":241961,"uid":17058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實意思係世界冇左你一個一樣會轉,但個世界就係因為有好多個你先會有呢個世界<br />\n唔可以冇左其中一樣<br />\n因為啱啱又loop鋼鍊一次,可能有滴滴1999</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鋼鍊係咪有兩套動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得好細個睇個套同FA好似唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新個套FA"},{"pid":"823331f2cd9c565130ee7048a167fee97324c896","tid":241961,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"冇咗一就唔係原本既全<br />\n全要有齊咁多個一先係全<br />\n<br />\n冇咗其中一個「一」，原本既全就唔存在<br />\n取而代之既係少咗一個「一」既全<br />\n<br />\nSOR FOR 1999"},{"pid":"bd1bdb31591a80ce7e1210552f23bc0a2bd80141","tid":241961,"uid":17058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇咗一就唔係原本既全<br />\n全要有齊咁多個一先係全<br />\n<br />\n冇咗其中一個「一」，原本既全就唔存在<br />\n取而代之既係少咗一個「一」既全<br />\n<br />\nSOR FOR 1999</blockquote><br />\n媽呀！！好深奧！！"},{"pid":"39ec8a741c491f9c1d3c82be13e23f0b0b90b516","tid":241961,"uid":13512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"滴乜鳩"},{"pid":"9a8dc090e1e31b1ee7ea9d9eaabde512f815243c","tid":241961,"uid":35118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"存在主意<br />\n<br />\n你認知的世界不可能左超越你的認知，因為你無法証明/認知其存在。你只能証明你的認知/consciousness。"},{"pid":"436423824205b642da755536df0c07e0aeacb4d7","tid":241961,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T18:53:04.000Z","msg":"其實句野可以好簡單，亦可以好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n因為只係edo師父拋出黎嘅一條問題，<br />\n唔同閱歷嘅人可以睇到唔同嘅野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋼鍊入面角色領悟到嘅大概同時亦有 弱肉強食、適者生存 嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n小學嗰時只係睇到 1 = 100%, 100% = 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；<br />\n中二時期覺得係 分久必合，合久必分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；<br />\n<br />\n推完Never7 之後覺得係 瞎子摸象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n即係呢句野可以應用喺世界觀度：<br />\n每個人其實只能夠認知到&quot;自己嘅世界&quot;，但係總係以為同其他人活喺同一個&quot;世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n(應該係 二元唯心論 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}